name: .CBF File Extension
summary: Learn about .CBF files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Custom calendar created with Calendar Builder, a calendar design program; includes an overall theme as well as custom borders, fonts, graphics, and icons that can be placed on each page of the calendar.

content: CBF files may be used for creating full size calendars, mini calendars, week planners, and day planners. Completed calendars can be printed directly from a home printer.
